HEADWORD: Proctocele
<hw>Proc"to*cele</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ anus +
<?/ tumor.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Inversion and prolapse of the
